==Media== ===Anime=== An [[anime]] television series by [[Toei Animation]] and [[Studio Gallop]] aired from October 2, 2018. The opening theme is "Bakutsuri Soul", performed by [[SymaG]] and the ending theme is "Yūjō ZABOOOON!!", performed by [[Mikako Komatsu]].<ref name="ANN1"/>
===Manga=== A [[manga]] series has been serialized in [[Shogakukan]]'s ''[[CoroCoro Comic]]'' since March 15, 2018.<ref name="ANN1"/>
===Video game=== A [[Nintendo 3DS]] game was released in March 2018. It consists of a [[barcode]] camera and a fishing reel accessory called a Bakutsuri Bar Rod. The game itself is a free download from the [[Nintendo eShop]]. The player uses the barcode camera on a barcode to open a [[fishing spot]], which allows them to fish for "bar soul" lifeforms.<ref name="Siliconera">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2018/01/21/bakutsuri-bar-hunter-makes-fish-creatures-barcodes-3ds/|title=Bakutsuri Bar Hunter Makes You Fish Creatures Out Of Barcodes With Your 3DS|website=Siliconera|date=January 21, 2018|accessdate=September 15, 2018}}</ref>
